/ content
.section
	.container.careers-title
		h1 
			span Graphic Designer/Illustrator (Part/Full Time) 	
			span.helper Full Time &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; . &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bangalore 
			a.btn href="#apply_Form" type="button" 
					| Apply <svg><use xlink:href="images/svgs/iconset.svg#icon-Right_Arrow"></use></svg> 
		p
			| Looking for a team member who would like to help build great products and add character to interface designs with outstanding iconography, illustrations and interactive concepts.
		h2
			| What are we looking for:
		ul.list
			li 
				| Modern illustrations and iconography style and ability to create vector illustrations 
			li
				| Passion/Interest in learning Interface Design
			li
				| Fundamental understanding of practices &amp; conventions for platforms like web, android &amp; iOS
			li
				|  Experience with tools like Illustrator, Wacom, Photoshop and After Effects

		h2
			| What will you get:
		ul.list
			li 
				| Get to work with a team with diversified skills on Visual Design, Product Design and Front-end Development. 
			li
				| A office that provides space to think, do and unwind.
			li
				| Freedom to experiment and innovate and have your say.
			li
				|  Always stay updated with latest design trends
		form.apply-form#apply_Form action="#" method="post"
			.group
		        input.textField#name type="text" 
		        span.highlight
		        span.bar
		        label.floating Name
		        p.message.msg1 Required
		        svg.cross-icon.crossOne
  					use xlink:href="images/svgs/iconset.svg#icon-delete_sign" 
			.group
		        input.textField#email type="text"
		        span.highlight
		        span.bar
		        label Email Address
		        p.message.msg2 Required
		        svg.cross-icon.crossTwo
  					use xlink:href="images/svgs/iconset.svg#icon-delete_sign" 
			.group
		        input.textField#behance type="text"
		        span.highlight
		        span.bar
		        label Behance/Website Link
		        p.message.msg4 Required
		        svg.cross-icon.crossFour
  					use xlink:href="images/svgs/iconset.svg#icon-delete_sign" 
			.group
		        textarea.textField#additionalInfo type="text" 
		        / placeholder="Add a covering Letter, tell us why you want to work with us or anything else you would like to share."
		        span.highlight
		        span.bar
		        label for="attachment" 
		    		| Cover letter
		    .group.last
	    		input#attachment type="file" multiple="mutiple"/
		    	label.fileupload for="attachment" 
		    		| Attach CV
		        p.message.attach-msg1 Required.
